lood specimen is clotted.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">too-old<a name=\"zw-rejection-reasons-too-old\"> </a></td><td>Specimen Too Old</td><td>Specimen transit time exceeded.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">haemolysed<a name=\"zw-rejection-reasons-haemolysed\"> </a></td><td>Haemolysed</td><td>Haemolysis detected.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">other<a name=\"zw-rejection-reasons-other\"> </a></td><td>Other</td><td>Other rejection reason.</td></tr></table></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
